    <p class="eyebrow reveal">Our Partners &amp; Affiliations</p>
    <h2 class="reveal reveal-delay-1">Proudly collaborating with leading organizations and initiatives to advance medical innovation</h2>
    <div class="partners-grid reveal reveal-delay-2">
      <div class="card card-white card-md partner-card">
        <img src="/assets/cpdmed.jpg" alt="CPD Med" class="partner-logo">
        <span class="partner-name">CPD Med</span>
      </div>
      <div class="card card-white card-md partner-card">
        <img src="/assets/startup-karnataka.jpg" alt="Startup Karnataka" class="partner-logo">
        <span class="partner-name">Startup Karnataka</span>
      </div>
      <div class="card card-white card-md partner-card">
        <img src="/assets/ktech.jpg" alt="KITS" class="partner-logo">
        <span class="partner-name">KITS</span>
      </div>
      <div class="card card-white card-md partner-card">
        <img src="/assets/make-in-india.jpg" alt="Make in India" class="partner-logo">
        <span class="partner-name">Make in India</span>
      </div>
      <div class="card card-white card-md partner-card">
        <img src="/assets/dpiit.jpg" alt="DPIIT" class="partner-logo">
        <span class="partner-name">DPIIT</span>
      </div>
      <div class="card card-white card-md partner-card">
        <img src="/assets/birac.jpg" alt="BIRAC" class="partner-logo">
        <span class="partner-name">BIRAC</span>
      </div>
      <div class="card card-white card-md partner-card">
        <img src="/assets/ccamp.jpg" alt="C-CAMP" class="partner-logo">
        <span class="partner-name">C-CAMP</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Careers -->
<section class="careers-hero" id="careers">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="eyebrow eyebrow-left eyebrow-accent">Careers</p>
    <h2 class="reveal">Build the future of kidney care</h2>
    <p class="careers-hero-lead reveal reveal-delay-1">
      We're a small team in Bengaluru working on one of the biggest unsolved problems in critical care.
      If you want your work to directly impact patient outcomes, we'd love to hear from you.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="careers-values">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="careers-values-grid">
      <div class="card card-light card-md careers-value-card reveal">
        <div class="careers-value-icon"><i class="ph-fill ph-heart-half" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
        <h4>Mission-driven</h4>
        <p>Every line of code, every sensor calibration, every clinical conversation is in service of detecting kidney injury earlier and saving lives.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card card-light card-md careers-value-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="careers-value-icon"><i class="ph-fill ph-puzzle-piece" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
        <h4>Full-stack problems</h4>
        <p>We build hardware, AI, and software together. You won't work in a silo — you'll see how your work connects to the entire system.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card card-light card-md careers-value-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="careers-value-icon"><i class="ph-fill ph-rocket-launch" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
        <h4>Early stage, high impact</h4>
        <p>We're pre-clinical and growing. Joining now means shaping the product, the culture, and the company from the ground up.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="careers-openings" id="open-positions">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="reveal">Open Positions</h2>
    <p class="section-description reveal reveal-delay-1">
      All roles are based in Bengaluru unless noted otherwise. We're flexible on hybrid arrangements.
    </p>
    <div class="careers-tile-grid">
      {% for job in collections.jobs %}
      <a href="{{ job.url }}" class="career-tile reveal">
        <div class="career-tile-content">
          <h3>{{ job.data.title }}</h3>
          <div class="career-tile-meta">
            <span><i class="ph-fill ph-map-pin" aria-hidden="true"></i> {{ job.data.location }}</span>
            <span><i class="ph-fill ph-clock" aria-hidden="true"></i> {{ job.data.type }}</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <i class="ph-fill ph-arrow-right career-tile-arrow" aria-hidden="true"></i>
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>

    <div class="careers-general reveal">
      <p>Don't see a perfect fit? We're always open to hearing from exceptional people. Send us a note at <a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}">{{ site.email }}</a> and tell us what you'd bring to Samaritan.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
